'''非游離輻射'''（{{Lang-en|Non-ionizing radiation}}）是指[[波長|波長]]较长、[[頻率|頻率]]较低、[[能量|能量]]低的[[射線|射線]]（[[粒子|粒子]]（主要是光子）或[[波|波]]的双重形式）或电磁波。[[輻射|輻射]]可分為[[游離輻射|游離輻射]]和非游離輻射，非游離輻射无法從（绝大多数）[[原子|原子]]或[[分子|分子]]裡面游離（{{lang|en|ionize}}）出[[電子|電子]]。<ref>{{cite web|date=16 July 2014|title=Ionizing & Non-Ionizing Radiation|url=http://www.epa.gov/radiation/understand/ionize_nonionize.html|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711115413/http://www.epa.gov/radiation/understand/ionize_nonionize.html|archive-date=11 July 2014|access-date=October 12, 2020|website=Environmental Protection Agency}}</ref>

